entries.femaleVariant: FIA approached me.
Listen, what if I told you... the FIA approached me about a gig?
Guessin' ya must've heard Space Force One crashed in Dogtown?
Was in Dogtown for a time. 'S right net to Night City, but it's like a whole 'nother world.
Rescued President Myers.
Was in Dogtown for a bit.
This thing with the FIA... if it works out, there might be a cure in it for me.
Good chance they could cure me.
The FIA? As in, the NUSA's intelligence agency? No shit.
God damn... Truly, you've outdone yourself, V. Heh, "secret agent" – the one thing missing from your resume.
Just as long as you know... governments, heads of state, all that? Even if you think they owe you for some reason, it usually boils down to them having something on you. So stay vigilant, OK?
Dogtown, huh. I think about it like a mistake, a regret. Nothing to do but wall it off, forget about it. Wait until it withers and dies.
Only... what if it's just one of their games? They're sure to know how much you're willing to risk…
It's a game, all right. Not about to let 'em turn me into their pawn, though. No worries, Panam, I'll manage.
Talk about it some other time, 'kay?
Talk later, I think..
There was talk, rumors, conspiracy theories. What of it?
This FIA agent... asked me for help. And now you're talkin' to the choom who rescued the president of the NUSA.
Yeah. Night City half pretends that Dogtown doesn't exist, but nobody can convince me there's not some kinda fucked up symbiosis between 'em.
Like a half-aborted Vegas for corpos and gangoons. What happens in Dogtown, stays in Dogtown. Heh, convenient.
What?! V, that's incredible!
I certainly hope so.
